{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow people to complete the Personal Independence Payment (PIP) form online",
        "additional_details": "As any disabled person will know, completing a PIP (Personal Independence Payment) form manually, in longhand, is exhausting, extremely stressful and is often physically painful. Please give us the option to complete the form online and allow us to save it as we are going along - so that we can return to it when we feel less exhausted. The Equality Act states that reasonable adjustments must be made for disabled people. Please allow this \u2018reasonable adjustment\u2019, to make our lives better.",
        "background": "The Government should allow people applying for Personal Independence Payment (PIP) to complete the form online after the initial call, and to be able to save it and come back to it.",
